data.description: Stunning, Well-Maintained Gem in the Heart of Las Vegas - NO HOA! This exquisite, 1.5-story home, features 4 beds/3 baths, tile flooring throughout, upgraded bathrooms, window coverings and ceiling fans. Step into the spacious living room, complete w/a cozy fireplace, perfect for creating memorable moments with family & friends. The primary bed & bath are located upstairs, creating a separate haven from the rest of the home. The 3rd bedroom is generously sized & could be split & converted into a 5th bedroom. The garage conversion has a closet & can serve as the 4th bedroom or a versatile game room/addt'l living area. The backyard is a private oasis, featuring a glistening pool, covered patio, & a large side yard. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, built-in oven, & plenty of cabinet space. Easy access to the Strip & conveniently located near the US-95 freeway, restaurants and shopping. This remarkable property won't last long, come and see this beauty before it's gone!
